-- SAC Said to Tell Clients It Received a Wells Notice From SEC
-- B y   K a t h e r i n e   B u r t o n
-- 2012-11-28T13:52:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-28/sac-said-to-tell-clients-it-received-a-wells-notice-from-sec.html
SAC Capital Advisors LP, the $14
billion hedge fund run by Steven Cohen, told clients on a
conference call today that it received a Wells Notice from the
U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission, according to a person
who listened to the call.  The person asked not to be named because the fund is
private.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katherine Burton in  New York  at 
 kburton@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
